    "- This will generate only `MAX_SAMPLES`\n",
    "- After you confirm everything works, you may change `RUN_FOREVER = True`\n",
    "\n",
    "Output files:\n",
    "- `live_stream_data.json`\n",
    "- `live_stream_data.csv`\n"
